        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Mumbai/scene_mongoose.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 5f86e15d-341c-4e21-ab8f-781c517dbe43).Image",
        "Description": "&quot;Mumbai Hero&quot;, Dawood Rangan&apos;s latest film is bound to be a hit. worryingly, they have been able to keep costs down by cutting corners on safety. In fact, Pa has already met her end when a balcony railing on the tower gave out and she plunged to her death bellow. \rOur Client, a rival director has asked us stop the production by eliminating two of the stars and the director, given Rangan is aware of just how unsafe the production is, you might be able to use that to your advantage. Good luck.",
